text: Asyanovo () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Asyanovsky Selsoviet, Dyurtyulinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 1,479 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 12 km from Dyurtyuli. == References == Category:Rural localities in Dyurtyulinsky District
title: Asyanovo
